data.title: UkiyaSeed's Other Blog
data.meta_description: Bandai Tamashii Nations posted official images of the S.H. Figuarts Devilman D.C. 50th Anniversary Ver. from the Mazinger Z vs. Devilman film.
data.text:
Bandai Tamashii Nations posted official images of the S.H. Figuarts Devilman D.C. 50th Anniversary Ver. from the Mazinger Z vs. Devilman film.

To promote the Japanese release of the Hellboy reboot film, Go Nagai's Dynamic Planning released a crossover image featuring Devilman and Hellboy.

â€‹Seven Seas Entertainment has unveiled the official covers of the first volumes of the Devilman: The Classic Collection and Captain Harlock: The Classic Collection manga volumes!

The official Devilman Crybaby anime website streamed the a new "special movie" of the upcoming anime. The video features the show's opening theme "Devilman no Uta" by Avu-chan, who will also voice Devil King Zenon in the show.

The official Netflix YouTube channel posted the trailer of the upcoming Netflix exclusive anime series, Devilman: Crybaby. The series commemorates the 50th anniversary of series creator Go Nagai's career.

Bandai Tamashii Nations unveiled the Figuarts ZERO Cyborg 009 vs. Devilman figure set. The figure is based on the Cyborg 009 vs. Devilman anime project.

Lantis posted in their official YouTube channel the preview for the Cyborg 009 vs. Devilman opening and ending theme songs. Said preview also featured new footage from the said project.

The full trailer for the Cyborg 009 vs. Devilman anime project has surfaced online. The trailer highlights some of the project's battles.
